Code preview of the table chatgroup

drop table if exists chatgroup;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: chatgroup */
/*==============================================================*/
create table chatgroup
(
group_id varchar(20) not null comment '每个群组有一个id',
id varchar(20) comment '1.每个用户唯一的标识
2.将通过该id号，寻找对应的xxx_info信息表，sport_record
,chatgroup
3.在业务逻辑中建议将id作为用户登录的账号来使用',
group_name varchar(10) not null comment '该群组的名称',
group_member varchar(100) not null comment '该群组的成员数组',
primary key (group_id)
);

alter table chatgroup comment '这是用来存储群组信息的表格';

alter table chatgroup add constraint FK_Reference_1 foreign key (id)
references account (id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
